snippet.title: BADASS TENNIS - App Preview
snippet.description:
BADASS TENNIS is like table tennis with explosions!  Play solo against the computer or go one-on-one against a friend across the table in VS mode!  BADASS TENNIS was created by Matt Hillmer in the Unity game engine and is available for free with no ads or in-app purchases on all major mobile platforms.

Get it on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/badass-tennis/id1567637341
Get it on Android (Google Play): https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.MattHillmer.BADASSTENNIS

Website: https://mattswebsite.net/badasstennis
